						<summary>

						<p>This inscription records the setting up of an image of Goddess for bed-chamber (<hi rend="italic">Paḷḷiarai nāchchiyār</hi>) by the order of the king and also gift of land for providing food offering to the goddess. The quantity of rice and other dishes to be offered are also specified.</p>						

